trans-unit.source: Specifies the mode for the automatic completion feature used in the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox"></xref> and <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TextBox"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Especifica o modo para o recurso de preenchimento automático usadas no <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox"> </xref> e <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TextBox"> </xref> controles.

trans-unit.source: Appends the remainder of the most likely candidate string to the existing characters, highlighting the appended characters.
trans-unit.target: Anexa o restante da cadeia de caracteres mais provável candidato para os caracteres existentes, realçando os caracteres acrescentados.

trans-unit.source: Disables the automatic completion feature for the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox"></xref> and <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TextBox"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Desabilita o recurso de preenchimento automático para o <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox"> </xref> e <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TextBox"> </xref> controles.

trans-unit.source: Displays the auxiliary drop-down list associated with the edit control.
trans-unit.target: Exibe a lista suspensa auxiliar associada ao controle de edição.

trans-unit.source: This drop-down is populated with one or more suggested completion strings.
trans-unit.target: Essa lista suspensa é preenchida com um ou mais cadeias de caracteres de preenchimento sugeridas.

trans-unit.source: Applies both <xref uid="langword_csharp_Suggest" name="Suggest" href=""></xref> and <xref uid="langword_csharp_Append" name="Append" href=""></xref> options.
trans-unit.target: Aplica-se tanto <xref uid="langword_csharp_Suggest" name="Suggest" href=""> </xref> e <xref uid="langword_csharp_Append" name="Append" href=""> </xref> opções.
